Introduction
============

WebIssues is a system supporting team collaboration across the Internet.
It can be used for storing bugs and other information with customizable
attributes, comments and file attachments. The server can be installed
on any host with PHP and MySQL or PostgreSQL. The client is a KDE
application which is faster and more comfortable than web-based
interfaces.

This application is the server for the WebIssues system.

Requirements
============

 * An HTTP server supporting PHP version 4.3 or newer
 * A MySQL or PostgreSQL database server

Installation
============

See INSTALL for detailed information about installing and upgrading
the server.

Contact
=======

Application website: http://webissues.mimec.org

Report bugs to: mimec@mimec.org
